Cheats are GTA IV cheats:

0 = unknown
1 = unknown (same as 0)
2 = Max Health and Armor
3 = Raise Wanted Level
4 = Lower Wanted Level
5 = unknown (does nothing)
6 = Change Weather
7 = Spawn Annihilator
8 = Spawn NRG 900
9 = Spawn FBI
10 = Spawn Jetmax
11 = Spawn Comet
12 = Spawn Turismo
13 = Spawn Cognoscenti
14 = Spawn Super GT
15 = Spawn Sanchez

Initially used in Max Payne 3, that's why we know the name.

0x48E92D3DDE23C23A.name: TASK_DISMOUNT_ANIMAL
0x48E92D3DDE23C23A.comment: Dismounts the ped from the animal it's mounted on. taskFlag affects what side the rider gets off. 1 << 18 will get off on the left side, where any other value will get off on the right side. The only other known value are 1 << 17 and 1 << 24, which has the behavior of any other value (getting off the animal from the right side). p2-p5 are almost always 0.

0xC4C32C31920E1B70.name: TASK_REACT
0xC4C32C31920E1B70.comment: Has the ped react to another entity. The reactionType determines how the ped reacts. p3 is 7.5f in the scripts. p4 is 0f. unkFlag is always 4. The rest of the parameters are unknown, but 0 is acceptable input. Here is a list of the different reaction type values by Mooshe: https://pastebin.com/Ju7BbmMt
